description: NagARam allows users to ask Alexa for an anagram of any single word from a list of 20,000 and will respond with the "best" anagram. Best is judged off of letter used from original word to build the new word. NagARam was the winning entry for the General Assembly Alexa Hackathon.
exampleInteractions: Tell me an anagram for bedroom.
name: Nag A Ram
shortDescription: NagARam allows you to ask Alexa for an anagram for over 20,000 words and she will return the best anagram.
